STATE
v.
HALL 2018-1572 Supreme Court of Ohio. January 23, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

APPEALS NOT ACCEPTED FOR REVIEW

Appellant's motion to dismiss or strike memorandum in opposition to jurisdiction denied. Appellee's motion to strike or in the alternative motion in opposition to appellant's motion to dismiss or strike memorandum in response to jurisdiction denied as moot.

Fischer, DeWine, and Donnelly, JJ., would deny appellant's motion to dismiss or strike memorandum in opposition to jurisdiction as moot.
